quran[111]{c,v,t}:
  2,142,"Arma ka Й“e fuyunngaaЙ“e e yimЙ“e mbi'a: \"E ko hucciЕӢtini Й“e ga'e Qibla maЙ“Й“e mo Й“e laatinoo e mu'un?\" Maaku: \"Ko Alla Woodani fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange, Himo Fewnira on Mo O Muuyi faade laawol focciingol"
  2,143,"Ko wano nii Men waЙ—iri on mofte hakindiiЙ—e fii yo on laato seedoytooЙ“e e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, NulaaЙ—o on seeditoyoo e dow mo'on. Men waЙ—iraa oo Qibla mo fewtataa e mu'un si wanaa no Men anndira on jokkoowo NulaaЙ—o on e on ruttotooЙ—o batte bonnere mu'un, hay si tawii Й—um laatike ko sattu-Й—um, si wanaa e dow Й“en Й“e Allah fewni. Allah Laatoraali yeeboowo liimanaaku mo'on: Pellet, Allah ko HilnotooЙ—o yimЙ“e Й“en Yurmee Й“e"
  2,144,"GomЙ—ii MeЙ—en Reeni waylitorgol yeeso maa ngon ka kammu. Ma Men Fewtinire Qibla waalaЕӢtooЙ—o ma:Fewtinir yeeso maaЙ—a ngon baЕӢЕӢe Juulirde HoormaЕӢteere nden.Nokku kala ko ngoЙ—on,fewtiniree geece mon Й—en baЕӢЕӢe mayru:Pellet,Й“en RokkaaЙ“e Defte Й“en no anndi [Al Qur'aanaare nden] ko nde goonga immorde ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e,Allah non siforaali WelsinsiiЙ—o e ko Й“e gollata"
  2,145,"Mi Woondii si a addanii Й“en rokkaaЙ“e deftere nden kala maande,Й“e jokkataa Qibla maa on,a wonaa jokkoowo Qibla maЙ“Й“e on,yoga e maЙ“Й“e wonaali jokkooЙ“e Qibla yoga.Mi Woondii si a jokkii mЙ“eleeЙ—e maaЙ“e Й“aawo kon ko ari e maa e anndal,pellet,an ontuma a jeyaama e tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  2,146,"ЖҒen Й“e Men Rokki Deftere nden hiЙ“e nganndiri Й—um wano Й“e nganndiri Й“iЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e; pellete, fedde goo e maЙ“Й“e hino suuЙ—ude goonga kan hara hiЙ“e nganndi"
  2,147,"Goonga kan ko ko ummori ko Joomi maa, wata a laatodu e Й“en sikkitiiЙ“e"
  2,148,"Ena woodani mo kala baЕӢЕӢe Й—e o fewtata e mun.Adondiree e moЖҙЖҙereeji,nokku kala ka laati-Й—on,Allah artiray on,on denndaangal. Pellete,Allah ko hattanЙ—o e dow kala huunde"
  2,149,"Nokku kala ka yaltirЙ—aa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, pellet, Й—um ko goonga ummoraade Joomi maa, Allah Wonaali WelsindiiЙ—o e kon ko gollo-ton"
  2,150,"Nokku kala ka yaltirЙ—aa, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon baЕӢЕӢe Suudu Hormorteendu ndun, nokku kala ka ngonЙ—on, fewtiniree geece mon Й—en baЕӢЕӢe mayru fii wata wonan yimЙ“e Й“en hujja e hoore mo'on - so wanaa Й“en tooГұuЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Wata non on huluЙ“e, Hulee Lam, fii no Mi Timminira neema Am On e mo'on, belajo'o on feeway"
  2,151,"Wano no Men Nuliri non e mo'on NulaaЙ—o ummoraade e mo'on,Himo janngana on Aayeeje Amen,himo laЙ“Й“ina on,himo anndina on Deftere nden,o anndina on ko on anndaana"
  2,152,"JaЕӢtee Lam, Mi Anndita on; jaarnee Lam wata on yeddam"
  2,153,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, wallitoree muГұГұaare e juulde. Pellet, Allah Hino Wonndi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,154,"Wata on wi'an Й“en wariraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en: \"ko Й“e maayЙ“e\". Ko woni, Й“en ko wuurЙ“e, kono on so'aa anndude"
  2,155,"Ma Men jaribo on huunde, immorde e kulol, e heege, e Й—uytagol jawle, e woЕӢkiiji, e dimЙ—e; Wewlin muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,156,"ЖҒen tawЙ“e si masiibo heЙ“iiЙ“e, Й“e wi'a: \"Menen dey ko Allah jeyi men, pellet to Makko menruttortoo"
  2,157,"ЖҒen Й—on, hino e dow maЙ“Й“e toraaje e yurmeende ummoraade ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko kamЙ“e ngoni feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  2,158,"Pellet,Safaa e Marwa ko jeyaaЙ—e e maandeeji [diine] Allah.Kala on hajjuЙ—o ka suudu [Kaaba], maa o waЙ—i Umra,ella woo fawaaki mo nde o wanngotoo hakkunde majji.On mo gattii moЖҙЖҙere,pellet Allah ko Jaarnoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,159,"Pellet, Й“en suudooЙ“e kon ko Men Jippini immorde e Й“anngannduyeeji e peewal, Й“aawo nde Men ЖҒannginani Й—um yimЙ“e Й“en ka Deftere, Й“en Й—on, Allah ena HuЙ—ude Й“e, huЙ—ooЙ“e Й“en na huЙ—ude Й“e"
  2,160,"Si wanaa Й“en tuubuЙ“e Й“e moЖҙЖҙini Й“e Й“aЕӢngini: Mi JaЙ“anay Й“en Й—on tuubuubuyee, ko Min Woni JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,161,"Pellet, Й“en yedduЙ“e Й“e maayi ko Й“e heereraaЙ“e, Й“en Й—on ena fawiiЙ“e kuddi Allah ndin e Malaa'ika en e yimЙ“e Й“en denndaangal"
  2,162,"Ko Й“e luttooЙ“e e magge. ЖҒe hayfinaЕӢtaake leЙ“te Й—en, Й“e wonaali nennanaЕӢteeЙ“e"
  2,163,"ReweteeЙ—e mon On ko ReweteeЙ—e Gooto. ReweteeЙ—o Alaa tanaa Makko, JurmotooЙ—o Yurmeende heeriinde e nde heeraaki Yurmeende"
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e Гұalorma on, e leЙ—Й—e dogirooje Й—en ka bahru nafugol yimЙ“e Й“en, e kon ko Allah Jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O Wurniri Й—um leydi ndin Й“aawo maayugol mayri O Saakti e mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli Й—in e duule eltaaЙ—e Й—en hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yimЙ“e haqqilooЙ“e"
  2,165,"Hino e yimЙ“e njogitiiЙ“e ko woori Allah yerondirЙ—i, hiЙ“e njiЙ—iraЙ—i wano Allah yiЙ—irtee, [ko] Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“uri saЙ—tude giggol wonande Allah. Hara Й“en tooГұuЙ“e annduno tuma Й“e nji'oyta lepte Й—en, wonde doole Й—en fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko SaЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanooЙ“e Й“en pottitoyii jokkunooЙ“e Й“en, Й“e nji'a lepte Й—en, sabuuji Й—in taЖҙira Й“e"
  2,167,"JokkunooЙ“e Й“en mbi'a: \"Hara nun fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora Й“e wano Й“e pottitori men nii\". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta Й“e golleeji maЙ“Й“e Й—in; hayrere e dow maЙ“Й“e, Й“e ngonaali njaltooЙ“e e yiite ngen"
  2,168,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e! Г‘aamee yoga e ko woni ka leydi ko dagii ko laaЙ“i, wata on jokku juri=taabe seytaane Й—in : Pellet, ko o gaГұo mo'on feeГұuЙ—o"
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paЕӢkare, e nde wowloton e hoore Allah ko on anndaa"
  2,170,"Si Й“e wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", Й“e mbi'a:\"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaЙ“e amen\";e hay si baabiraaЙ“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en haqqilataa hay e huunde Й“e haanditaaki"
  2,171,"Misal Й“en yedduЙ“e hino wa'i wa on ewnotooЙ—o kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko faaЙ—uЙ—i, mumiЙ—uЙ—i, wumuЙ—i; kaЕӢji Й—i haqqiltaa"
  2,172,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e! Г‘amee immorde e laaЙ“uЙ—i Й—i Men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko KaЕӢko rewoton"
  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jiiЙ“e, e ЖҙiiЖҙam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duГұaaЙ—o [e Гұaamugol Й—um] hara wanaa Й“ewЙ—o wanaa jaggituЙ—o, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotooЙ—o YurmeteeЙ—o"
  2,174,"Pellet Й“en suuЙ—ooЙ“e ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hiЙ“e soodira Й—um cogguwel famЙ—ungel. ЖҒen Й—on alaa waЙ—ude ka deedi maЙ“Й“e si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa Й“e Гұalnde darngal, O LaЙ“Й“iЕӢtaa Й“e, hino woodani Й“e lepte muusuЙ—e"
  2,175,"Ko Й“en ngoni soodirЙ“e majjere nden peewal, e lepte Й—en ya'fuyee. kaawse ko muГұГұoriЙ“e ka yiite"
  2,176,"ЖҠuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii Deftere nden goonga. pellet Й“en luutondirЙ“e e Deftere nden Й“e ngonii e lurral woЙ—Й—ungal"
  2,177,"Dewal ngal wonaali fewtiЕӢgol geece mon Й—en Й“aЕӢnge fuЙ—naange e hiirnaange. Ko woni tun dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—inЙ—o Alla e Г‘alaande sakkitiinde nden, e Malaa'ika en, e Deftere nden, e AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en; o okki jawdi -e hoore yiЙ—ugol ndi- joomiraaЙ“e Й“adondiral, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“illiiЙ“e Й“en, e Й“ii hoore-laawol, e Й“en torotooЙ“e, e fii rinЙ—inngol daaЙ—e; o niiЙ“ni juulde, o totti asakal, e Й“en hunnooЙ“e aadondiral maЙ“Й“e si Й“e haldidaama, e Й“en muГұГұitooЙ“e ka baasi e ka lorra, e fewndo gowole. Ko Й“en ngoni goonguЙ“e Й“en, ko Й“en kadi ngoni gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,178,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e,njottiigu farlaama e mo'on:dimo sabu dimo, jeyaaЙ—o sabu jeyaaЙ—o,deyel sabu deyel.Kala ya'fanaaЙ—o goЙ—Й—um e musiЙ—Й—o makko,ko jokkitirogol no moЖҙЖҙiri tottira e makko no moЖҙЖҙiri.ЖҠum Й—oo ko hoynaneede immorde e Joomi mo'on e yurmeende.Kala on jaggituЙ—o Й“aawo Й—u'um,no woodani mo lepte muusuЙ—e"
  2,179,"No woodani on ka njottiigu nguurdam, yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqilaaji. Belajo'o on wonay gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,180,"Farlaama e mo'on:si maayde nden arii e mo'on,si o accii jawle: wasiyanagol jibinЙ“e mo Й“en,e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri.Ko hannduyee e dow gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,181,"Kala on waylituЙ—o Й—um Й“aawo o nannde, pellet bakkaatu mun on ko Й“en waylituЙ“e fawii. Allah ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,182,"On mo huli ooГұaare immorde e wasiyiiЙ—o maa bakkaatu o moЖҙЖҙini hakkunde maЙ“Й“e,bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Pellet Alla ko Yawtanoowo YurmotooЙ—o"
  2,183,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, koorka kan farlaama e mo'on wano ka farliranoo e Й“en adinooЙ“e on, Й“elajo'o laatoЙ—on gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,184,"Г‘alЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. Kala e mo'on laatiiЙ—o nawnuЙ—o maa e hoore-jahal: ko limtugol ГұalЙ—i goo. No fawii Й“en haЙ—tanЙ“e ka, Гұammingol Й“iliiЙ—o. Kala on gattuЙ—o moЖҙЖҙere Й—um no moЖҙЖҙani mo. Ko nde hooroton Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, si wonii hiЙ—on nganndi"
  2,185,"Lewru koorka ndun, ndu Alqur'aanaare nden jippinaa e mu'un, ko ndu peewal wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en e Й“angannduyeeji immorde e peewal e serndugol. On e mo'on seediiЙ—o lewru ndun, yo o hooru ndu. On tawЙ—o no nawni maa himo e hoore-jahal, ko limtugol e ГұalЙ—i goo. Alla no Faandanii on neweende O Faandanaaki on saЙ—teende; e fii yo on timmin limoore nden e no mawniniro Alla kon ko O Fewni on, belajo'o on jaarnay Mo"
  2,186,"Si jeyaaЙ“e Am Й“en lamndike lan fii Am, hary Min: Ko Mi ЖҒaЙ—iiЙ—o. MiЙ—o Jaabina toraare torotooЙ—o si o torike Lam. Yo Й“e nooto Lam, e yo Й“e gomЙ—inam, belajo'o Й“e feeway"
  2,187,"Daginanaama on jemma koorka kan yiidugol e rewЙ“e mon Й“en. Ko Й“e koltu mo'on ko on koltu maЙ“Й“e. Alla Anndii wonde on laatinoke jaЕӢfotooЙ“e ko*e-mon,O JaЙ“ani on tuubuubuyee O Ya'fii on.Jooni non,soccondiree e maЙ“Й“e Й—aЙ“Й“on ko Alla Winndani on.Г‘aamee yaron haa gaarawol danewol ngol Й“aЕӢngirana on Й“alewol ngol ka peeral, refti timminiron koorka kan jemma. Wata on soccondir e maЙ“Й“e hara ko on ufniiЙ“e ka juulirЙ—e.ЖҠum ko keeri Allah, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й—i.Ko wano nii Allaahu On ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta yimЙ“e Й“en aayeeje Makko Й—en,belajo'o Й“e wona gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,188,"Wata on Гұaamir jawle mon Й—en hakkundeeji mo'on e hoore mehre, werloron Й—e e ГұaawooЙ“e Й“en fii yo fedde goo Гұaamira e jawle yimЙ“e Й“en bakkaatu, hara hiЙ—on nganndi"
  2,189,"HiЙ“e naamno-maa fii darorЙ—e lebbi, wi'u: \"ЖҠin ko waqaЕӢtinanayЙ—i yimЙ“e e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngardaЕӢton cuuЙ—i Й—in immorde ka Й“abbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—uЙ—o.Ngardanee cuuЙ—i Й—in ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol Й“en haЙ“ooЙ“e on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,191,"wareeЙ“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e, yaltineeЙ“e nokku ka Й“e yaltiniri on: ko geddi Й—in Й“uri mawnude e dii haЙ“ugol ngol. Wata on haЙ“uЙ“e ka Misiide HormaЕӢteere haa Й“e haЙ“a on e mayre. Si Й“e haЙ“ii on haЙ“ee Й“e. Ko wano nii woni njoЙ“di heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  2,192,"Si Й“e haЙ—itike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yumeende"
  2,193,"HaЙ“ee Й“e haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa Й“en tooГұooЙ“e"
  2,194,"Si Й“e haЙ“ii on e lewru hormaЕӢteeru, haЙ“ee Й“e e lewru hormaЕӢteeru, horminaaЙ—i Й—in ko yottondirtee Й—um. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow mooЙ—on. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,195,"WiЕӢtee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juuЙ—e mon Й—en faade e halakuyee. MoЖҙЖҙinee, pellet Alla no YiЙ—i moЖҙЖҙinayЙ“e Й“en"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon Й—en haa kirse Й—en yottoo nokku majje. On tawЙ—o e mo'on ko ГұawЙ—o maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo heЙ“aali, ko hoorugol balЙ—e tati ka hajju e jeeЙ—iЙ—i si on ruttike; Й—en ko sappo timmuЙ—e. Ko jaЕӢtaa koo, ko fii on tawЙ—o Й“eynguure mun nden laataaki hoЙ—uЙ“e ka Misiide hormaЕӢte. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaaЙ—i. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollugЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, Allah no Anndi Й—um.YooЙ“ee,ko Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e njooЙ“a,ko gomЙ—al. Hulee Lam yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde Й—aЙ“Й“oton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaЕӢtee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. JaЕӢtoron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muuЙ—um ko on jeyaaЙ“e e majjuЙ“e"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimЙ“e Й“en yahri Й—on, InsinanoЙ—on Alla. Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaЕӢtoree innde Alla wano jaЕӢtorton baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, maa ko Й“uri Й—um tiiЙ—ude. No e yimЙ“e Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara geЙ“al-moЖҙЖҙal"
  2,201,"No e maЙ“Й“e wi'ooЙ“e: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"ЖҒen Й—on, no woodani Й“e geЙ“al-moЖҙЖҙal e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Alla ko YaawuЙ—o hasboore"
  2,203,"JaЕӢtee Innde Alla e ГұalЙ—i limtaaЙ—i. On yaccinЙ—o e nder balЙ—e Й—iЙ—i, bakkaatu fawaaki mo; on neЙ“tinЙ—o kadi, bakkaatu fawaaki mo.Wonannde on gomЙ—uЙ—o. Hulee Alla, nganndon pellet ko ka Makko mooЙ“indiroyte-Й—on"
  2,204,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en on mo konngol mun no haawne ka nguurdam aduna, himo seediЕӢtina Alla kon ko woni e ndeer Й“ernde makko, hara non ko kaЕӢko Й“uri saЙ—tude wennje"
  2,205,"Si o huccitii, o yaha ka leydi fii o bonnu e mayri, o halka gese e geГұГұi. Alla YiЙ—aa bononda"
  2,206,"Si o wi'anaama: \"Hulu Alla\", mawniЕӢtinaare heЙ“a mo sabu bakkaatu. Jahannama yonii mo, e nge bonii ndaЙ—Й—udi"
  2,207,"No e yimЙ“e Й“en: on mo no sooЙ—tira woЕӢkii mun kin Й—aЙ“Й“ugol yarluyee Alla. Alla ko HilnotooЙ—o jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en"
  2,208,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e, naatiree e lislaamu ka denndanngal, wata on jokku juri seytaane Й—in. On ko gaГұo mooЙ—on Й“aЕӢnguЙ—o"
  2,209,"Si on ooГұike Й“aawo koo ko ari on e Й“aЕӢngannduyeeji, nganndee pellet, Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,210,"Taw si Й“ee no sabbii: si wanaa nde Allaahu On ArdaЕӢta Й“e e ndeer niЙ“e duule wondude e Maalaa'ika en; fiyaaku gasinee. Ko ka Alla woni ruttorde fiyakuuji Й—in"
  2,211,"Naamno geЙ—alЙ“e Israa'iila en:ko jelu woni ko Men Rokki Й“e e maandeeji Й“aЕӢnguЙ—i! Kala waЙ—tituЙ—o neema Alla on Й“aawo on arude mo, pellet, Alla ko TiiЙ—uЙ—o lepte"
  2,212,"Nguurdam aduna Й—am cuЙ—inanaama Й“eya heeferЙ“e, hiЙ“e jalkita Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e. ЖҒen gomЙ—uЙ“e wonoyay dow maЙ“Й“e Гұalnde darngal. Alla no Arsikira on Mo O Muuyi, ko aldaa e hasboore"
  2,213,"YimЙ“e Й“en laatino mofte goote. Allaahu On Nuli AnnabaaЙ“e Й“en, wewlinooЙ“e e jeertinooЙ“e, O Jippindini e maЙ“Й“e Deftere nden hoore goonga, fii yo o Гұaawu hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en kon ko Й“e luuondiri e muuЙ—um. Luutondiraali e muuЙ—um, si wanaa Й“en rokkaaЙ“e nde, Й“aawo kon ko ari Й“e e Й“aЕӢngannduyeeji; ka bewre hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Allah Fewniri duЕӢyee Makko Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e kon ko Й“e luutondiri e muuЙ—um, immorde e goonga. Alla No Fewna on Mo O Muuyi, faade e laawol focciingol"
  2,214,"Kaa on sikku on naatay aljanna hara araali on sugu kon ko arunoo Й“en wuliiЙ“e on? HeЙ“iino Й“en saЙ—tteende e lorra, Й“e dillinaa haa NulaaЙ—o wi'i, e Й“en gomЙ—indimЙ“e e makko: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ballal Alla ngal?\", hey, pellte ballal Alla ngal Й“aЙ—tiingal"
  2,215,"ЖҒe ngaray naamnaade ma ko honЙ—um Й“e sakkotoo, wi'u: \"Si won ko sakkiЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, ko fii jibinЙ“e on, e Й“adondiraaЙ“e Й“en, e wonduЙ“e Й“en, e Й“iliiЙ“e Й“en, e seteeЙ“e Й“en. kalako golluЙ—on e moЖҙЖҙere, pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o Й—um"
  2,216,"Hare nden farlaama e mo'on; nden non ko aГұaande e mo'on,no tijjaa ka aГұoton huunde hara ko nde moЖҙЖҙere mon, no tijjaa kadi ka yiЙ—oton huunde hara ko nde bone mon. Ko Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,217,"HiЙ“e naamno maa fii lewru hormaЕӢte ndun, haЙ“ugol e mayru, maaku: \"HaЙ“ugol e mayru ko mawnu-Й—um. Ko sakkagol e laawol Alla ngol e yeddugol Mo e Misiide hormorde nden e yaltingol yimЙ“e mayre Й“en e mayre, Й“uri mawnude ka Alla. Ko shirku on kadi Й“uri mawnude dii wargol ngol; Й“e seerataa hiЙ“e haЙ“a on haa Й“e rutta on e diina mon, si Й“e haaЙ—tanii. Kala e mo'on yaltondirЙ—o e diina mu'un, o maayi ko o keefeero: Й“en Й—on, golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en bonii aduna e laakara; ko Й“en ngoni yimЙ“e yiite, Й“en ko luttooЙ“e ton"
  2,218,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e e Й“en feruЙ“e haЙ“iri fii laawol Alla, Й“en Й—on no jortii Yurmeende Alla; Alla ko Ya'fotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,219,"HiЙ“e naamno-maa fi sanngara e karte, maaku: \"No e Й—in Й—iЙ—i bakkaatu mawЙ—o e nafawoy wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, ko bakkaatu majji on non Й“uri mawnude e dii nafawoy majji on\". HiЙ“e naamno-maa kadi hol ko Й“e sakkotoo? Maaku: \"yaafuya=Ko fawi e haaju\". Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Й—en, belajo'o on miijitoto"
  2,220,"Fii aduna on e laakara on, hiЙ“e naamno-maa fii wonduЙ“e Й“en, maaku: \"Ko moЖҙЖҙagol e maЙ“Й“e Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude\". Si on jillondirii e maЙ“Й“e, ko musiЙ—Й“e mo'on. Alla no Anndi on moЖҙЖҙinoowo e on bonnoowo. Si Alla muuyuno, O ЖҒiЙ—tinanayno on. Pellet Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,221,"Wata on resu Й“en rewЙ“e shirkayЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina: Mi Woondii ko korЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin Й“en worЙ“e shirkooЙ“e haa Й“e gomЙ—ina: Mi Woondii ko maccuЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.ЖҒen Й—on hiЙ“e nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duЕӢyee Makko. Himo ЖҒaЕӢngina Aayeeje Makko Й—en wonannde yimЙ“e Й“en, belajo'o Й“e wa'ajitoto"
  2,222,"HiЙ“e naam-no maa fii fiilordu, maaku: ЖҠum ko nefinii Й—um; luncitee rewЙ“e Й“en fewndo fiilordu, wata on Й“aЙ—to Й“e haa Й“e laaЙ“a. Si Й“e laaЙ“ii, ngaree e maЙ“Й“e nokku ka Alla Yamiri on Й—on. Pellet Alla No YiЙ—i tuubayaЙ“e Й“en Himo YiЙ—i kadi Й“en laЙ“Й“inotooЙ“e"
  2,223,"RewЙ“e mon Й“en ko gese mo'on. Ngardee e ngesa mon mbam nokku kala ka faaliraЙ—on, ngardinanee woЕӢkiiji mon Й—in. Hulle Alla, nganndon ko on kawrooЙ“e e Makko. Weltin gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en"
  2,224,"Wata on waЙ—u Alla heedo fii ngoondooje mon Й—en; nde Й—iggoton, gomЙ—on hulon moЖҙЖҙinon hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,225,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on gardambi=bolle mehre ka ngoondooje mo'on, kono Himo Nanngitira on kon ko Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en faggitii. Alla ko Hafroowo MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  2,226,"No woodani Й“en woondirooЙ“e suddiiЙ“e mun Й“en: habbitagol lebbi nayi. Si Й“e ruttike, pellet Alla ko Haforoowo HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,227,"Si Й“e fellitii ceergal ngal, pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,228,"SeeraaЙ“e Й“en yo habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e Й—en laaЙ“e tati; dagaЕӢtaako Й“e suuЙ—ugol kon ko Alla Tagi ka ndeer renngaaji maЙ“Й“e, si wonii hiЙ“e gomЙ—imЙ“e Alla e Гұalaande sakkitiinde. Ko moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e jojjidi ruttugol Й“e e Й—um, si hawrii hiЙ“e faalaa weldital. No woodani Й“en [rewЙ“e] yeru kon ko fawiiЙ“e, no moЖҙЖҙiri. No woodani worЙ“e Й“en: Й“ural e dow maЙ“Й“e. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,229,"Ceergal, ko laaЙ“i Й—iЙ—: ko jogitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitira no moЖҙЖҙiri. DagaЕӢtaako on Жҙettitugol huunde e kon ko rokku-Й—on Й“e, si wanaa hara Й“e hulii [kamЙ“e Й—iЙ—o] nde Й“e niiЙ“nataa keeri Alla Й—in. Si on hulii roЕӢkude ГұiiЙ“nude keeri Alla Й—in, goopi alanaa Й“e e kon ko debbo on soktori. ЖҠin ko keeri Alla, wata on jaggitu-Й—i. kala jaggituЙ—o keeri Alla Й—in, ko Й“en ngoni tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,230,"Si o seerii mo, on [debbo] dagitaЕӢtaako mo Й“aawo Й—u'um, haa o resindira e gorko goo. Si on [gorko] seerii mo, goopi fawaaki Й“e nde Й“e ruttondira, si Й“e fellitii ГұiiЙ“nugol keeri Alla Й—in.ЖҠin ko keeri Allah, Himo ЖҒaЕӢnginana Й—i Й“en yimЙ“e ngannduЙ“e"
  2,231,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike: jogitoree-Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri maa accitoron Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Wata on jogitor Й“e lorrugol nde jaggitoton. Kala waЙ—uЙ—o Й—um, gomЙ—ii o tooГұii hoore-makko. Wata on jogitor Aayeeje Alla Й—en jalnori. Annditee neemaaji Alla Й—i O Neemini e mo'on, e ko O Jippini e mo'on immorde e Deftere e Г‘eeГұal; Himo Wa'ajora Й—um. Hulle Alla, nganndon pellet Alla ko AnnduЙ—o kala huunde"
  2,232,"Si on seerii rewЙ“e Й“en, laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en yottike, wata on laagu Й“e nde moodiЙ“Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en resata Й“e; si Й“e welondirii hakkunde maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. ЖҠum no waajoree on tawЙ—o e mo'on no gomЙ—ini Alla e Г‘alaande Sakkitiinde. Ko jaЕӢtanaЙ—on koo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙannde on, Й“uri laaЙ“aande. Alla No Anndi onon on nganndaa"
  2,233,"JibimЙ“e Й“en yo muynin Й“iЙ—Й“e maЙ“Й“e Й“en duuЙ“i Й—iЙ—i timmuЙ—i; wonannde on faandiiЙ—o timminde muyninngol ngol.No fawii jibinanaaЙ—o on, Гұammingol holitinira [rewЙ“e] Й“en no moЖҙЖҙiri. WoЕӢkii woo fawaaka si wanaa ko ki waawata. Wata jibinЙ—o on lorrire sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, wanaa jibinanaaЙ—o on kadi lorrirtee sabu Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on; no fawii ronoowo on yeru Й—um. Si Й“e faandike entude e hoore yarlondiral hakkunde maЙ“Й“e e diisondiral, bakkaatu fawaaki Й“e. Si on faandike Й—aЙ“Й“ude muyninanoowo on Й“iЙ—Й“e mon Й“en, bakkaatu fawaakii on, si on jonnirii kon ko Й“en [muyninooЙ“e] hanndi e moЖҙЖҙere.Hulee Alla, nganndon ko O ReenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,234,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: yo Й“en habbiЕӢtin ko'e maЙ“Й“e lebbi nayi e balЙ—e sappo. Si Й“e yottike laje maЙ“Й“e Й—en, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri. Alla Ko HumpitiiЙ—o kon ko golloton"
  2,235,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko weeЙ“itoton, e sabboyde suddiiЙ“e Й“en, maa suuЙ—uЙ—on Й—um ka woЕӢkiiji mo'on. Alla No Anndi aray ka annditon fii maЙ“Й“e, ko woni tun, wata on fodondir e maЙ“Й“e [desal] e gunndoo: si wanaa nde wowloton koЕӢngol moЖҙЖҙol, wata on fellitu humugol dewgal ngal haa lajal edda ngal yottoo. Ngande pellet Alla No Anndi ko woni e woЕӢkiiji mo'on, ReЕӢtee e Makko, nganndon pellet Alla Ko Haforoowo MuГұГұiiЙ—o"
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on renndude e maЙ“Й“e maa jaЕӢtanagol Й“e teЕӢe, dakmitee Й“e:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol Й“e no moЖҙЖҙiri.Hannduyee fawiiЙ—o moЖҙimЙ“e Й“en"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on meemude Й“e, tawa on jaЕӢtanike Й“e teЕӢe: ko feccere kon ko jaЕӢti-Й—on, si wanaa hara Й“e ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juuЙ—e mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afotoЙ—on Й“urata Й“aЙ—tinnde gomЙ—al. Wata on yejjitu Й“ural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko ReenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e julЙ—e Й—en, e julde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖҙЖҙiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖҒen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕӢgol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖҙЖҙere. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖҙЖҙiri. ko goongofawiiЙ—o gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖҒaЕӢnginiraЕӢta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o on haqqilay"
  2,243,"E a tinaali Й“en njaltunooЙ“e e galleeji mu'un, kamЙ“e ko Й“e guluuje, ka reenagol e maayde, Allaahu On Daalani Й“e: \"Maayee\", refti O Wuurniti Й“e? Pellet Alla ko Jom ЖҒural e dow yimЙ“e Й“en, ko woni tun, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en njaanataa [Alla]"
  2,244,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla Ngol, nagndon pellet Alla ko Nanoowo AnnduЙ—o"
  2,245,"Ko hombo woni on Гұawloowo Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere, O Sowitana mo nde cowalle Й—uuЙ—uЙ—e? Alla No ЖҒiЙ—ttina Himo YaГұГұa, ko faade ka Makko ruttete-Й—on"
  2,246,"E a tinaali ngun mbatu Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'ila, Й“aawo Muusaa, tuma nde Й“e wi'annoo Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on: \"Imminan men lamЙ—o, men haЙ“a fii laawol Alla Ngol?\" O maaki: \"Hara on tijjaaki si hare nden farlaama e mo'on nde roЕӢkoton haЙ“ude?\" Й“e mbi'i: \"Ko haЙ—ata men haЙ“ugol e fii laawol Alla Ngol, gomЙ—ii men njaltinaama e galleeji amen e Й“iЙ—Й“e amen?\" Nde hare nden farlanoo e maЙ“Й“e, Й“e hucciti, si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Alla Ko AnnduЙ—o tooГұooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,247,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e:\"Alla Imminanii on Taaluuta laamЙ—o\". ЖҒe mbi'i:\"Hol no laamu laatoraЕӢta mo e hoore amen,ko menen Й“uri mo haandude e laamu,o rokkaaka yaajeende jawdi?\" O maaki:\"Alla SuЙ“ike mo e dow mo'on,O ЖҒeydi mo yaajeende ka ganndal e ka Й“anndu\". Alla No Rokka Laamu Makko Ngun on Mo O Muuyi,Alla ko YaajuЙ—o [Й“ural] AnnduЙ—o"
  2,248,"Annabaajo maЙ“Й“e on maakani Й“e: \"Nganndee Maande Alla nden, ko nde Arkawal ngal arata on; deeЖҙere no e ndeer maggal, immorde ka Joomi mo'on, e ko heddinoo ko aalo Muusaa e aalo Haaruuna en acci, hara Malaa'ika en no ronndii ngal. Pellet no e koo ko jaЕӢtaa Й—oo, Maande wonannde on; si o laatike gomЙ—imЙ“e"
  2,249,"Nde Taaluuta yaltidunoo e konu ngun, o maaki: \"Alla No Jarribora on caangol: kala yarЙ—o e maggol o jeyaaka e am, kala mo meЙ—aali ngol ko on Й—on jeyaa e am, si wanaa on ГұeЙ—irЙ—o junngo mun ГұeЙ—annde\". ЖҒe yari e caangol ngol si wanaa seeЙ—aaЙ“e e maЙ“Й“e. Nde o lummbunoo ngol, kaЕӢko e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e wonduЙ“e e makko, Й“en mbi'i: \"Feere alanaa en e Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun\". ЖҒen fellituЙ“e hawray e Alla Й“en mbi'i: \"Heewii ka fedde tokosere fooliri fedde Й—uuЙ—unde, duЕӢayee Alla\". Pellet Alla No Wondi e muГұГұiiЙ“e Й“en"
  2,250,"Nde Й“e feeГұannoo Jaaluuta e konu mun ngun, Й“e mbi'i: \"Joomi amen, Rufu muГұal e dow amen, TabiЕӢtinaa teppe amen, Faabo-Й—aa men e Й“ee heeferЙ“e"
  2,251,"ЖҒe fooliriЙ“e DuЕӢayee Alla: Daawuuda wari Jaaluuta, Alla Rokki mo Laamu e Annabaaku, O Anndini mo kon ko O Muuyi. Si wanaano Ko Alla DuГұirnoo yimЙ“e Й“en yoga e dow yoga, leydi ndin bonayno. Kono Alla Ko Jom ЖҒural e dow winndere nden"
  2,252,"ЖҠen ko Aayeeje Alla, MeЙ—en JaЕӢnga Й—e e dow maaЙ—a wondude e Goonga, Pellet ko a jeyaaЙ—o e NulaaЙ“e Й“en"